1.Create a spring boot project on start.spring.io project with Web and Spring Security dependency added,
2. Add dependency for  JWT
<!-- https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/io.jsonwebtoken/jjwt -->
<dependency>
    <groupId>io.jsonwebtoken</groupId>
    <artifactId>jjwt</artifactId>
    <version>0.9.1</version>
</dependency>
3.Add JwtUserDetailsService.java class for setting your credential.
4.Create below class to configure your userDetail service to be used by spring security.
@Configuration
 public class SecurityConfiguration {....}
